trans-unit.source: Returns the TRC as an array of shorts. If the profile has specified the TRC as linear (gamma = 1.0) or as a simple gamma value, this method throws an exception, and the getGamma() method should be used to get the gamma value. Otherwise the short array returned here represents a lookup table where the input Gray value is conceptually in the range [0.0, 1.0]. Value 0.0 maps to array index 0 and value 1.0 maps to array index length-1. Interpolation may be used to generate output values for input values which do not map exactly to an index in the array. Output values also map linearly to the range [0.0, 1.0]. Value 0.0 is represented by an array value of 0x0000 and value 1.0 by 0xFFFF, i.e. the values are really unsigned short values, although they are returned in a short array.
trans-unit.target: 以短裤数组形式返回TRC。如果配置文件已将TRC指定为线性（gamma = 1.0）或作为简单的gamma值，则此方法将引发异常，应使用 getGamma() 方法获取gamma值。否则，此处返回的short数组表示一个查找表，其中输入的Gray值在概念上在[0.0，1.0]范围内。值0.0映射到数组索引0，值1.0映射到数组索引 length-1 。插值可用于为输入值生成输出值，这些输入值未精确映射到数组中的索引。输出值也线性映射到[0.0，1.0]范围。值0.0由数组值0x0000表示，值1.0由0xFFFF表示，即，这些值实际上是无符号的短值，尽管它们是在短数组中返回的。
